cates and important correspondence, etc.<br \/>\nThe National Library and Archives pays particular attention to awareness of the personal archive.\u00a0 In addition to the public interest in reducing material losses resulting from the loss and damage of personal documents, there is also a historical.\u00a0 Many of the community members possess personal documents that are of great importance at the national level so their preservation becomes a national priority rather than personal.\u00a0 As a result, spreading awareness among students about the importance of documents conservation will get every Emirati home acquainted with the importance preserving documents so they all can participate in building the Nation&#8217;s memory.\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Student Archive Organization And Method Have you ever provided your students with a large amount of review papers and asked them to keep them in a special file?\u00a0 How do students save their academic papers throughout the year?\u00a0 What is the best way to save and organize papers to be used later by students?\u00a0 How [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":458,"parent":451,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"templates\/template-with-banner.php","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/457"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=457"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/457\/revisions"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\